RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT a.contract_ref_no,a.product_code FROM tltbs_position_contract a,oltbs_contract b WHERE a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no AND b.branch = global.current_branch AND NVL(b.department_code,'*') = NVL(global.current_branch ,'*') AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM olvw_avl_prod_br_usr WHERE product_code = a.product_code AND branch_code = global.current_branch AND user_id = global.user_id)
